###This script can be run interactively and non-interactively, 

	##Running interactively:

	Simply execute the script from command line from within the /scripts directory #perl cloudwatch.pl or #perl /scripts/cloudwatch.pl. A menu will popup and ask questions.

	##Running non-interactively
	The script accepts 2 arguments cloudwatch(rds dbidentifier) or cloudwatch(ec2 deviceid) , so on the sysadmin box, pass the command perl /scripts/cloudwatch.pl <rds> <dbidentifier> or perl /scripts/cloudwatch.pl <ec2> <deviceid>

